title: Drake - One Dance (Solidisco Remix)
description:
Solidisco - One Dance (ft Gayatri Nair) [DRAKE COVER]

As soon as we heard Drake had sampled Kala & Crazy Cousins on his 'One Dance' record, we knew we had to flip it back into a house record for our sets. We went on youtube to make sure no one had done it yet and that's when we came across Gayatri's cover of the track. She killed it (at only 14 years old btw) and we immediately changed gears and wanted to create a new version of the song from scratch based on her take. A couple emails and a few days of work later and here's what came out.
